abstract: NBA Roundup; Golden State Warriors defeat Denver Nuggets, 118-105; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Brook Lopez and Jarrett Jack combined for 55 points to lead the Nets over the Celtics, who had beaten them by 25 points two days earlier.

headline.main: Warriors Top Nuggets; 15-0 Start Ties Record
